37:12.646 --> 37:16.048
Hello? Hey...

37:16.050 --> 37:19.017
<i>I had to bring Stevie on,
help me answer the phones.</i>

37:19.019 --> 37:21.421
- Hey, Grundy, what's happening?
- Of course, I got a line on it.

37:21.423 --> 37:24.625
No, I'm lousy, my fucking ear
is like a piece of shit.

37:24.627 --> 37:26.794
Yeah, I got the lines.

37:26.796 --> 37:29.499
