53:06.507 --> 53:07.838
He got punched in the face.

53:07.840 --> 53:09.374
Well, kids get into fights, man.

53:09.376 --> 53:11.443
Not when they're with adults.

53:11.445 --> 53:13.679
You told him he could get into
