53:20.654 --> 53:22.555
I told him within reason.

53:22.557 --> 53:25.091
Was that before or after you
told him...

53:25.093 --> 53:26.725
that he would never play
pro baseball?

53:26.727 --> 53:29.796
That I was just being on the
