53:34.769 --> 53:36.002
Let him have this.

53:36.004 --> 53:37.803
All right, look, I'm sorry.

53:37.805 --> 53:39.839
He said he wanted to get his
name on the Wall of Fame...

53:39.841 --> 53:42.011
