53:44.479 --> 53:47.483
You really think he could
get his name on the wall?

53:48.750 --> 53:50.818
Maybe if he, if he pitches
well...

53:50.820 --> 53:52.985
for the rest of the season
then... maybe.

53:52.987 --> 53:56.356
He really pitched well?

53:56.358 --> 53:58.425
He did.

53:58.427 --> 54:02.362
Okay, fine, but none of this
depressing shit.

54:02.364 --> 54:03.797
No problem.

54:03.799 --> 54:06.400
