54:06.402 --> 54:08.068
Of course.

54:08.070 --> 54:10.007
I'll get you your beer.

54:15.445 --> 54:18.912
JOHN (V.O.): <i>Remember when
I told you that everything...</i>

54:18.914 --> 54:21.017
<i>in my life eventually went
to shit?</i>

54:27.124 --> 54:30.024
Back him up, and give me
