I'm running for city office?
I talk to people.

55:50.744 --> 55:52.644
They voice their concerns.

55:52.646 --> 55:56.747
The other day, I'm going door to
door and somehow I ended...

55:56.749 --> 56:01.619
at Adam Kramer's, he tells me
that his TV got stolen...

56:01.621 --> 56:03.120
