too much.

56:48.070 --> 56:51.804
Am I? Maybe I'll run it
by Adam Kramer.

56:51.806 --> 56:54.708
Good luck running anything
by Adam Kramer.

56:54.710 --> 56:58.747
But then I'll try Chief Taggart
when I meet with him next week.

56:58.749 --> 57:02.252
See how many recent robbery
victims bet through you.

57:10.193 --> 57:12.162
MATT: Thank you much.

57:18.234 --> 57:23.873
Hey, what's it going to take?

57:23.875 --> 57:26.342
- What?
- What do you want?

57:26.344 --> 57:32.083
Campaign contribution. You want
a cut, cash, what do you want?

57:34.085 --> 57:36.121
I want you to do
the right thing.

57:40.692 --> 57:42.561
<i>(ENGINE STARTING)</i>

57:53.638 --> 57:55.108
