breathing.

01:00:10.849 --> 01:00:14.751
You're not far away from an
oxygen tank if you're wondering.

01:00:14.753 --> 01:00:16.888
Thank you.

01:00:20.758 --> 01:00:22.758
Doc?

01:00:22.760 --> 01:00:25.862
